Find and plot missingness in the data 







    
    







    


pct_list = []
for col in df.columns:
    pct_missing = np.mean(df[col].isnull())
    if round(pct_missing*100) >0:
        pct_list.append([col, round(pct_missing*100)])
    print('{} - {}%'.format(col, round(pct_missing*100)))
